title: Employments in the Netherlands 2020
summary: Overall Labor force in millions has increased over the Year.
Labor force in millions is slightly increasing from 2016 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Labor force in millions, about 8.78 was reported at Year 2018
The lowest Labor force in millions, of value 8.4 was reported at Year 2016
